sentences.english: Cannot change text flow because columns will overflow into margins .
sentences.chinese: 不能改变文字排列，因为栏将溢出到页边距中。

sentences.english: A finger or stylus interrupts the light beams and position is determined on the grid.
sentences.chinese: 一只手指或者尖笔打断轻的梁，位置是决定闸极栏。

sentences.english: Use this page to edit a column of this discussion board.
sentences.chinese: 使用此网页可编辑此讨论板的栏。

sentences.english: Hebei Jinbiao mesh Co. , Ltd. , is the production of highway fencing wire mesh.
sentences.chinese: 栏河北金标网栏有限公司，是生产高速公路护栏网。

sentences.english: Type headings flush against the left margin of the relevant column.
sentences.chinese: 标题保持与相应栏的左边界齐平。

sentences.english: You will be able to swap hotbar configurations at the same time you swap specs.
sentences.chinese: 切换天赋时，可以同时切换快捷栏设置。

sentences.english: The brakes let go and the car crashed through the bushes at the edge of the town common, gathering speed.
sentences.chinese: 刹车松开了，汽车碾过了镇边缓冲速度的绿化栏。

sentences.english: In order to export the sidebar, the main content area is temporarily stretched vertically.
sentences.chinese: 为了导出侧边栏，主体区域现在暂时的使用垂直拉伸。

sentences.english: For each good described in Box 7, identify the HS tariff classification to six digits.
sentences.chinese: 第七栏的每种货物应填写《协调制度》六位数编码。

sentences.english: This sort of impassible terrain has no grid overlaid on it.
sentences.chinese: 这类不觉疼痛的地形没有在它上涂上的闸极栏。

sentences.english: If noise reduction is enabled, an information bar will display in the report.
sentences.chinese: 如果启用降噪，会在报告中显示一个信息栏。

sentences.english: Tariff quota concessions will be implemented according to the date specified in the "implementation" column.
sentences.chinese: 关税配额减让将按照“实施”栏中列明的日期实施。

sentences.english: A sliding sidebar on the left-hand side displays a page switcher with thumbnail previews.
sentences.chinese: 左边栏的滑动条还可以显示带预览图的分页切换。

sentences.english: The bank debited ￡10 from Mr Smith's account.
sentences.chinese: 银行把一笔十镑的帐记入史密斯先生借方栏。

sentences.english: The applications tab displays launchers for the software installed on the system.
sentences.chinese: 程序标签栏显示了系统内所安装软件的启动项。

sentences.english: Smart toolbar, always knows what you want.
sentences.chinese: 智能工具栏，总是知道你想要什么。
